{"tid":1771701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯獲中国政法大學頒發名譽博士學位","createTime":"2019-12-06T05:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T09:54:54.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c1fb6266ef7d98f1fd4cc0d234c04a43f93f2057","tid":1771701,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:02:43.000Z","msg":"《環球時報》報道，立法會議員何君堯獲中國政法大學頒發名譽博士學位，以表彰他在法律界的卓越貢獻及成就。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯十月底被母校，英國安格里亞魯斯金大學撤銷其榮譽法學博士學位。校方當時表示，擁有該校名譽學位的人士，需要作為該校學生、舊生、職員及該校所服務社群的榜樣。校方表示，何君堯的言行愈來愈令人關注，經過調查之後，校方決定撤回何君堯名譽博士學位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496255-20191206.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496255-20191206.htm&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScFGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=df836f09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496255-20191206.htm&h=72790ef3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496255-20191206.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e585e00a68e3880f4b3ce0619fd536e1d1d2e296","tid":1771701,"uid":14503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:04:19.000Z","msg":"中國博士都垃圾黎"},{"pid":"cb32bc30404900eebe4f9a5b1770ce07d77f2296","tid":1771701,"uid":256246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:05:24.000Z","msg":"恭喜被大灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f5642c01b95834cebe44894e4d6fe402f5bfb7","tid":1771701,"uid":158771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e585e00a68e3880f4b3ce0619fd536e1d1d2e296","tid":1771701,"uid":14503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:04:19.000Z","msg":"中國博士都垃圾黎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:05:38.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以話我知何妖係法律界有咩成就？"},{"pid":"f7a6a477df5f6934bfc3acaeef98d52a438df194","tid":1771701,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T05:08:03.000Z","msg"